      "text": "OpenAI Codex v0.114.0 (research preview)\n--------\nworkdir: C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud\nmodel: gpt-5.4\nprovider: aiproxy\napproval: never\nsandbox: danger-full-access\nreasoning effort: high\nreasoning summaries: none\nsession id: 019d778b-b423-7483-b087-186e00ae3c7d\n--------\nuser\nYou are a senior architect reviewing an implementation plan (Phase 2.5 — a small follow-up to Phase 2, which has already shipped).\r\n\r\nRead these files:\r\n1. C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md — Phase 2.5 implementation plan (3 Tasks / 1 Batch)\r\n2. C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-design.md — Phase 2.5 design document (references Phase 2 as frozen)\r\n3. C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/CLAUDE.md — project rules\r\n\r\nReference (read as context, do not re-review):\r\n- Phase 2 plan: C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-plan.md (already shipped, commits 7a5ecfb..549e298)\r\n- Phase 2 design: C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-design.md (frozen, [实现完成])\r\n\r\nPhase 2.5 scope: Clean up 2 test_debt items from Phase 2 Contract Pack — (a) focus-mode node/edge fading via graph.setElementState, (b) cross-module badge hover tooltip via G6 Tooltip plugin. Bridge/contrast edge display is explicitly dropped (no data model support).\r\n\r\nPerform plan review per checklist:\r\nA. 自洽性: Task 依赖完整、接口契约一致、无逻辑矛盾、破坏性操作有回滚\r\nB. 代码库对齐: 引用路径真实、不违反现有 API、不命名冲突、不重复功能\r\n  - Verify ConceptMapPanel.vue 当前实际结构与 plan 中引用的 API（computed/watch/defineExpose/createGraph）一致\r\n  - Verify @antv/g6 v5.1.0 的 setElementState / Tooltip plugin API 签名与 plan 中示例代码匹配\r\n  - Verify edge id 'edge-' 格式与 buildG6Data 现有实现一致\r\nC. 架构适配: 职责单一、依赖方向正确、接口隔离、配置集中、单功能变更影响 ≤3 文件\r\nD. 完整性: 每个行为变更 Task 须有测试契约段（5 字段）和边界条件段（至少 3 个）、测试契约质量\r\nD+. 测试契约质量（test-gap 硬判定）:\r\n   - 逻辑镜像测试（测试只是实现的对称复述，不能在错误实现下失败）→ test-gap HIGH\r\n   - 无入口级验证（测试只调内部函数，不经过用户可触达的入口）→ test-gap MED\r\n   - 无反例说明（测试契约未写明\"错误实现会怎样失败\"）→ test-gap MED\r\n   - 特别审查 CE-004/CE-005/CE-006 的反证断言是否真的能打中各自声称的破坏点\r\nE. 风险评估: Tier 分级有据、高风险区域标记\r\nF. Contract Pack 完整性:\r\n   - invariants INV-006..INV-010 是否每条有 test_ref 映射到具体测试\r\n   - counter_examples CE-004..CE-006 是否每条有 mitigation 对应实际测试\r\n   - test_debt 对 Phase 2 的两条原条目处置是否清晰（resolved / deferred）\r\n   - 桥接/对比边作废的理由是否技术合理\r\nG. 视觉/感知任务特别关注:\r\n   - Phase 2.5 属视觉任务，autonomy-boundary 规定验收权在用户\r\n   - plan 是否明确了\"不得自行声明视觉验收通过\"\r\n   - plan 是否列出用户手动验证步骤\r\n\r\n**审查规范（必读）：** 先读以下文件中的对应段落：\r\n- Finding 分类: ~/.claude/rules-t3/review-templates.md <!-- anchor: finding-classification -->\r\n- Finding Type: ~/.claude/rules-t3/review-templates.md <!-- anchor: finding-type -->\r\n- PASS/FAIL 判定: ~/.claude/rules-t3/review-templates.md <!-- anchor: pass-fail -->\r\n- test-gap 判定: ~/.claude/rules-t3/review-templates.md <!-- anchor: test-gap-criteria -->\r\n- 行为变更守卫: ~/.claude/rules-t3/review-templates.md <!-- anchor: behavior-change-guard -->\r\n\r\nOutput structured findings with: ID, Severity, Category, Type (defect_fix/behavior_change), Before-behavior, After-behavior, Evidence (file:line), Impact, Repair hypothesis (optional, advisory only).\r\n\r\nRed flag watch: Phase 2.5 的 state 命名（'faded'/'dimmed'/'emphasized'）是否与 G6 v5.1 保留状态冲突？setElementState 调用时机（nextTick vs 同步）是否存在竞态？Tooltip plugin 的 enable 谓词是否会在非节点元素（如 edge）上误触发？\r\n\r\nConclude with PASS or FAIL.\r\nWrite in Chinese.\nmcp: filesystem starting\nmcp: filesystem ready\nmcp startup: ready: filesystem\ncodex\n按你的清单做计划审查。我先读取审查规则、Phase 2.5 计划/设计、项目规则，以及当前代码里 `ConceptMapPanel.vue`、`buildG6Data` 和 G6 版本/API 定义，先确认事实基线再出 finding。\nexec\n\"C:\\\\Windows\\\\System32\\\\WindowsPowerShell\\\\v1.0\\\\powershell.exe\" -Command \"Get-Content -Path C:\\\\Users\\\\Administrator\\\\edu-cloud\\\\docs\\\\plans\\\\2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-design.md\" in C:\\Users\\Administrator\\edu-cloudexec\n\"C:\\\\Windows\\\\System32\\\\WindowsPowerShell\\\\v