tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L69), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:87](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L87), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:190](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L190), [phase2.5-plan.md:46](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L46), [phase2.5-plan.md:75](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L75), [phase2.5-plan.md:322](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L322), [phase2.5-plan.md:352](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L352)\nImpact: 按计划原样实施，功能和测试都对不上当前代码；若强行新增 prop，又把已上线的内部焦点机制改成外部接口，属于未请求的接口漂移。\nRepair hypothesis: 保持焦点源为内部 `focusedNodeId`，新增逻辑改为依赖/监听该 `ref`，测试从现有 `graph` 事件入口或已暴露实例状态驱动。\n\n2. `F002`\nSeverity: `HIGH`\nCategory: `code-bug`\nType: `behavior_change`\nBefore-behavior: 当前 `defineExpose` 暴露 `crossModuleBadges`、`crossModulePeers`、`focusedNodeId`、`clearFocus`；现有 Phase 2 测试已依赖这组暴露接口验证焦点交互。\nAfter-behavior: 计划的三处 `defineExpose` 示例都把 `focusedNodeId` / `clearFocus` 从暴露集合中删掉，只保留新增字段。\nEvidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:289](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L289), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:208](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L208), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:229](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L229), [phase2.5-plan.md:102](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L102), [phase2.5-plan.md:360](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L360), [phase2.5-plan.md:603](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L603)\nImpact: 会直接破坏现有已上线/已验证的测试契约，属于回归风险，不满足“Phase 2 frozen”前提。\nRepair hypothesis: `defineExpose` 只能增量扩展，必须保留 `focusedNodeId` 和 `clearFocus`。\n\n3. `F003`\nSeverity: `MEDIUM`\nCategory: `code-bug`\nType: `defect_fix`\nBefore-behavior: 当前 `buildG6Data()` 先按可见节点过滤边，再在过滤后的数组上生成 `edge-${i}`。\nAfter-behavior: 计划里的 `relatedEdgeIds` 和 `stateMap` 都按 `props.edges` 原始索引生成 `edge-${i}`，并声称“与 buildG6Data 严格一致”。\nEvidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:178](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L178), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:181](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L181), [phase2.5-plan.md:86](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L86), [phase2.5-plan.md:92](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L92), [phase2.5-plan.md:337](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L337), [phase2.5-plan.md:440](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L440)\nImpact: 一旦出现不可见边或后续过滤条件变化，`setElementState` 会命中错误 edge id，相关/无关边强调会错位。\nRepair hypothesis: 把 edge id 生成规则抽成单一 helper，`buildG6Data` 和 `relatedEdgeIds` 共用同一份“过滤后边列表”。\n\n4. `F004`\nSeverity: `MEDIUM`\nCategory: `code-bug`\nType: `defect_fix`\nBefore-behavior: 当前组件在 `moduleId/nodes/edges` 变化时会 `destroyGraph() -> createGraph()`，且 `moduleId` 之外不会自动清空焦点。\nAfter-behavior: 计划声明“createGraph/destroyGraph 生命周期保持原样”，同时只新增 `focusedNodeId` 变化监听，不在 graph 重建后重放状态。\nEvidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:271](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L271), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:276](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L276), [phase2.5-plan.md:349](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L349), [phase2.5-plan.md:815](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L815)\nImpact: 焦点 overlay 仍开着时如果发生 refresh 或 nodes/edges 更新，新 graph 会恢复默认样式，出现“已聚焦但未淡化”的视觉失真。\nRepair hypothesis: 在每次 `createGraph()`/`graph.render()` 后，如果存在焦点，补一次 `updateElementStates()`。\n\n5. `F005`\nSeverity: `HIGH`\nCategory: `test-gap`\nType: `defect_fix`\nBefore-behavior: `INV-007/INV-008` 与 `CE-005` 声称要验证 `graph.setElementState(...)` 的真实调用和清空分支。\nAfter-behavior: 计划测试没有断言任何真实 `setElementState` 调用，只是改一个不存在的 prop、检查 `relatedNodeIds`，或断言 `updateElementStates()` “不抛异常”。\nEvidence: [phase2.5-plan.md:400](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L400), [phase2.5-plan.md:413](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L413), [phase2.5-plan.md:430](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L430), [phase2.5-plan.md:783](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L783), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:7](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L7)\nImpact: 这是 review-templates 里明确定义的逻辑镜像测试，`updateElementStates` 就算完全不调 `graph.setElementState` 也可能绿；`CE-005` 不能证明“退出焦点会清状态”。\nRepair hypothesis: 扩展现有 G6 mock，给实例补 `setElementState` spy；通过真实入口触发焦点进入/退出，再断言最后一次调用参数。\n\n6. `F006`\nSeverity: `HIGH`\nCategory: `test-gap`\nType: `defect_fix`\nBefore-behavior: `INV-009` 应验证真实 `Tooltip` plugin 已挂到 `Graph` 配置上，且 `enable/getContent` 与实际 wiring 一致。\nAfter-behavior: 计划直接在测试里手写一个“等价的” `enablePredicate`，完全不读取 `new Graph({...}).plugins` 中的真实配置。\nEvidence: [phase2.5-plan.md:569](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L569), [phase2.5-plan.md:676](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L676), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:7](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L7), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:181](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L181)\nImpact: 就算 plugin 根本没注册、`trigger` 写错、`key` 写错、`getContent` 没接 `crossModulePeers`，测试也能通过；`INV-009` 不能证明真实用户入口可用。\nRepair hypothesis: 直接读取 `graphCtorCalls[0].plugins[0]`，断言 `type/key/trigger`，并调用其 `enable/getContent`。\n\n7. `F007`\nSeverity: `MEDIUM`\nCategory: `design-concern`\nType: `defect_fix`\nBefore-behavior: 用户要求和设计开头都把桥接/对比边视为“显式放弃”，设计前文还写了 `resolved-not-applicable`。\nAfter-behavior: 设计后文与 plan Contract Pack 又把同一条 debt 标成 `deferred` 到 Phase 3。\nEvidence: [phase2.5-design.md:24](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-design.md#L24), [phase2.5-design.md:75](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-design.md#L75), [phase2.5-design.md:263](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-design.md#L263), [phase2.5-plan.md:804](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L804)\nImpact: Contract Pack 对 test debt 的最终处置不清晰，Gate 无法判断这条是“关闭”为 N/A，还是“保留”到 Phase 3。技术理由本身是合理的，但状态标签必须统一。\nRepair hypothesis: 在 design 与 plan 里统一为一种处置语义，并与用户口径一致。\n\n**Checklist 摘要**\n\n- `A 自洽性`: `FAIL`。焦点状态契约写成 prop，与现状和自身测试入口都不自洽；桥接/对比边处置也前后冲突。\n- `B 代码库对齐`: `FAIL`。`ConceptMapPanel.vue` 当前实际结构与 plan 的 `props.focusedNodeId` / `defineExpose` 假设不一致；`edge-${i}` 规则也未按现实现过滤后索引对齐。\n- `B API 核对`: `setElementState` overload 与 `Tooltip.enable` 签名已核实匹配本地 `@antv/g6 5.1.0`；但 `Tooltip.getContent` 在本地 d.ts 中是 `Promise<HTMLElement|string>`，且 design 里的 `graph.getElementDataById?.(...)` 不是公开 `Graph` API。\n- `C 架构适配`: 部分通过。变更面仍是 2 文件，但 graph 重建后不重放状态，会让视觉行为与生命周期脱节。\n- `D 完整性`: 形式上 3 个 Task 都有 5 字段测试契约和 ≥3 条边界条件。\n- `D+ 测试契约质量`: `FAIL`。Task 2 和 Task 3 明显命中“逻辑镜像测试”与“无入口级验证”；`CE-005` 反证断言打不中其声称的破坏点，`CE-006` 相对成立。\n- `E 风险评估`: 部分通过。`risk_modules` 有标注，但没有明确 Tier 分级依据。\n- `F Contract Pack`: 部分通过。`INV-006..010` 都有 `test_ref`，`CE-004..006` 都有 mitigation；但 `CE-005` mitigation 无法证明目标行为，桥接/对比边的 debt disposition 不一致。桥接/对比边因缺数据模型而不做，这个技术理由本身是合理的。\n- `G 视觉/感知任务`: `PASS`。plan/design 都明确了“不得自行声明视觉验收通过”，并给出了用户手动验证步骤。\n\n**结论**\n\n`FAIL`\ntokens used\n126,565\n**Findings**\n\n1. `F001`\nSeverity: `HIGH`\nCategory: `code-bug`\nType: `behavior_change`\nBefore-behavior: 当前组件的焦点态是内部 `ref`，由 `node:click` / `clearFocus` / `focusPeer` 驱动，未声明 `focusedNodeId` prop。\nAfter-behavior: 计划把焦点源改成 `props.focusedNodeId`，并要求测试用 `wrapper.setProps({ focusedNodeId: ... })` 驱动。\nEvidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:69](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L69), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:87](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L87), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:190](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L190), [phase2.5-plan.md:46](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L46), [phase2.5-plan.md:75](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L75), [phase2.5-plan.md:322](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L322), [phase2.5-plan.md:352](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L352)\nImpact: 按计划原样实施，功能和测试都对不上当前代码；若强行新增 prop，又把已上线的内部焦点机制改成外部接口，属于未请求的接口漂移。\nRepair hypothesis: 保持焦点源为内部 `focusedNodeId`，新增逻辑改为依赖/监听该 `ref`，测试从现有 `graph` 事件入口或已暴露实例状态驱动。\n\n2. `F002`\nSeverity: `HIGH`\nCategory: `code-bug`\nType: `behavior_change`\nBefore-behavior: 当前 `defineExpose` 暴露 `crossModuleBadges`、`crossModulePeers`、`focusedNodeId`、`clearFocus`；现有 Phase 2 测试已依赖这组暴露接口验证焦点交互。\nAfter-behavior: 计划的三处 `defineExpose` 示例都把 `focusedNodeId` / `clearFocus` 从暴露集合中删掉，只保留新增字段。\nEvidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:289](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L289), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:208](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L208), [ConceptMapPanel.test.js:229](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/__tests__/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.test.js#L229), [phase2.5-plan.md:102](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L102), [phase2.5-plan.md:360](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L360), [phase2.5-plan.md:603](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L603)\nImpact: 会直接破坏现有已上线/已验证的测试契约，属于回归风险，不满足“Phase 2 frozen”前提。\nRepair hypothesis: `defineExpose` 只能增量扩展，必须保留 `focusedNodeId` 和 `clearFocus`。\n\n3. `F003`\nSeverity: `MEDIUM`\nCategory: `code-bug`\nType: `defect_fix`\nBefore-behavior: 当前 `buildG6Data()` 先按可见节点过滤边，再在过滤后的数组上生成 `edge-${i}`。\nAfter-behavior: 计划里的 `relatedEdgeIds` 和 `stateMap` 都按 `props.edges` 原始索引生成 `edge-${i}`，并声称“与 buildG6Data 严格一致”。\nEvidence: [ConceptMapPanel.vue:178](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L178), [ConceptMapPanel.vue:181](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/frontend/src/components/knowledge-tree/ConceptMapPanel.vue#L181), [phase2.5-plan.md:86](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L86), [phase2.5-plan.md:92](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L92), [phase2.5-plan.md:337](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L337), [phase2.5-plan.md:440](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-10-teacher-workbench-phase2.5-plan.md#L440)\nImpact: 一旦出现不可见边或后续过滤条件变化，`setElementState` 会命中错误 edge id，相关/无关边强调会错位。\nRepair hypothesis: 把 edge id 生成规则抽成单一 helper，`buildG6Data` 和 `relatedEdgeIds` 共用同一份“过滤后边列表”。\n\n4. `F004`\nSeverity: `MEDIUM`\nCategory: `code-bu